PrecisEnactment of an ORDER PROHIBITING ENTRY ON CERTAIN LANDS IN THE YUKON TERRITORY (1999, No. 3) - which prohibits the staking of mineral claims or prospecting for precious minerals on a total of some 261.77 hectares of land situate in the Village of Teslin and at the Pine Lake Airfield, near the Rancheria River and Daughney Lake Road, for airport purposes.
